    <%= render partial: "home/shared/accordion_item", locals: {
      title: "What can I sell on Gumroad?",
      content: "Digital products, e-books, courses, tutorials, and memberships—almost anything! Creators in just about every industry use (and love) Gumroad, from digital artists, writers, musicians and other creative-types to business-minded entrepreneurs and tech gurus like our SaaS creators. A better question is, \"What can't I sell on Gumroad?\""
